{
  "stem": "2118.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we marched-- we didn't go with the main highways because we were afraid of the American airplanes that [? we'd ?] be shoot up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we were between trees and we just pushed them into the trees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, it was dark at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One time, I remember we sat behind on a field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was like an [? abutment. ?] Like, you know, like it's going down on the ground.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was a big pipe coming out of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Must've been a pipe from refuse or whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And a guy climbed into that pipe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- and then when-- they counted us every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then when we went up-- when we stood up to march, they counted us and a guy was missing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And how could he get away in the middle of a field with no-- so they figured out he went into the pipe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they shot into the pipe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But he survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because he suddenly-- the pipe bent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It had a bend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he climbed-- when he heard the first shot, he-- he climbed behind the bend and he survived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then one time, we came to a little town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we went into-- it was after a hard night's working or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They let us into the giant barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they didn't count us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And either they-- they felt-- they forgot the count or they loss the count or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Next morning, when we went out, one guy hid in the barn in the rafters-- he hid someplace.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I don't know exactly where.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they took us out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they counted us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we had a figure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we went maybe a mile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And for some reason, they changed their mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they took us back.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
